'''伞形花内酯'''也译为'''伞形酮'''（{{lang-en|Umbelliferone}}，也称为'''7-羟基香豆素'''，{{lang|en|7-hydroxycoumarin}}）是一种[[天然产物|天然的]][[香豆素|香豆素]]类化合物，最早发现于[[伞形科|伞形科]]植物，因而得名，有抗氧化活性<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.chemicalland21.com/lifescience/phar/UMBELLIFERONE.htm|title= UMBELLIFERONE|work= www.chemicalland21.com|access-date= 21 November 2011|archive-date= 2020-09-19|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200919011119/http://www.chemicalland21.com/lifescience/phar/UMBELLIFERONE.htm}}</ref><ref name="pmc">{{cite journal | title = Anti-inflammatory and antioxidant effects of umbelliferone in chronic alcohol-fed rats | authors = Sim MO, Lee HI, Ham JR, Seo KI, Kim MJ, Lee MK | journal = Nutr Res Pract | year = 2015| volume = 9| issue = 4| pages =364-369 | doi = 10.4162/nrp.2015.9.4.364| pmid = 26244074 | pmc = 4523479}}</ref>，可用作[[防曬油|防曬油]]<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1016/j.tetlet.2008.03.063 | pmid=19081820 | title=Rational design of a fluorescent hydrogen peroxide probe based on the umbelliferone fluorophore | journal=Tetrahedron Letters | date=2008 | volume=49 | issue=19 | pages=3045–3048 | first=Lupei | last=Du| pmc=2490821 }}</ref>。

它可由[[2,4-二羟基苯甲醛|2,4-二羟基苯甲醛]]和[[丙二酸|丙二酸]]为原料反应制得。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Current Organic Synthesis|volume=16|issue=1|language=en|date=2019-02-04|pages=130–135|doi=10.2174/1570179415666180924124134|url=http://www.eurekaselect.com/165598/article|title=Temperature Dependent Green Synthesis of 3-Carboxycoumarins and 3,4-unsubstituted Coumarins|accessdate=2021-02-01|author=Jack van Schijndel, Dennis Molendijk, Luiz Alberto Canalle, Erik Theodorus Rump, Jan Meuldijk}}</ref>[[乙酰基间苯二酚|乙酰基间苯二酚]]和[[丙烯酸甲酯|丙烯酸甲酯]]在[[乙酸钠|乙酸钠]]和[[甲酸|甲酸]]的存在下（[[乙酸亚铑|乙酸亚铑]]催化）反应，也可得到产物。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=The Journal of Organic Chemistry|volume=80|issue=22|language=en|issn=0022-3263|date=2015-11-20|pages=11544–11550|doi=10.1021/acs.joc.5b01713|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acs.joc.5b01713|title=Rh-Catalyzed Synthesis of Coumarin Derivatives from Phenolic Acetates and Acrylates via C–H Bond Activation|accessdate=2021-02-01|author=Sunita K. Gadakh, Soumen Dey, Arumugam Sudalai|archive-date=2017-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170525120542/http://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acs.joc.5b01713}}</ref>它和[[乙酸酐|乙酸酐]]反应，可以得到乙酰基伞形花内酯<!-- CAS 10387-49-2 -->。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Talanta|volume=170|language=en|date=2017-08|pages=119–127|doi=10.1016/j.talanta.2017.03.102|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0039914017303971|title=A fluorescent homogeneous assay for myeloperoxidase measurement in biological samples. A positive correlation between myeloperoxidase-generated HOCl level and oxidative status in STZ-diabetic rats|accessdate=2021-02-01|author=Pierre Stocker, Mathieu Cassien, Nicolas Vidal, Sophie Thétiot-Laurent, Sylvia Pietri|archive-date=2018-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615232123/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0039914017303971}}</ref>
